'''Pottersville''' is an [[unincorporated community]] in [[Franklin Township, Owen County, Indiana|Franklin Township]], [[Owen County, Indiana|Owen County]], in the [[U.S. state]] of [[Indiana]].<ref name="GNIS">{{cite web | url = {{GNIS3|441507}} | title = Pottersville, Indiana | work = [[Geographic Names Information System]] | publisher = [[United States Geological Survey]] | accessdate = July 19, 2017}}</ref>

==History==
Pottersville was laid out in 1858.<ref>{{cite book | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1VLWAAAAMAAJ&pg=PA763#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=Counties of Clay and Owen, Indiana: Historical and Biographical | publisher=F.A. Battey & Company | author=Blanchard, Charles | year=1884 | pages=763}}</ref>

==Geography==
Pottersville is located at {{coord|39|12|26|N|86|48|51|W|type:city}}.

